  "detailed_description": "TowerMancer, a challenging strategy tower building game. Gather resources, build rooms, face menacing threats and meet The Lich family!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453400/extras/f3ae37f8e9c9dc739ff052302c8ec0e5.webp?t=1765546070\" width=512 height=45 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453400/extras/c84aa9f93df77ea0dc2a19e2eaaf2251.webp?t=1765546070\" width=18 height=18 /></span> 15 Campaign Levels <br>Follow the TowerMancer story becoming the powerful being that he is destined to!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453400/extras/c84aa9f93df77ea0dc2a19e2eaaf2251.webp?t=1765546070\" width=18 height=18 /></span> 18 Challenges <br>Branches and side contracts will challenge your skills against all the odds!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453400/extras/c84aa9f93df77ea0dc2a19e2eaaf2251.webp?t=1765546070\" width=18 height=18 /></span> 2 Game Modes (Campaign / Random Mode)<br>Meet the Lich family and fulfill contracts to become a master of your trade, or sharpen your skills in random contracts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453400/extras/c84aa9f93df77ea0dc2a19e2eaaf2251.webp?t=1765546070\" width=18 height=18 /></span> Unlockables <br>Venturing with side contracts may award you benefits to assist you in this journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453400/extras/e26ea43e77b60aa8434c6735778b3302.webp?t=1765546070\" width=512 height=44 /></span><br><br> Long ago The Lich, the most powerful mage of the underworld... found love within the cold grasp of The Lichmancer, a necromancer whose powers could rise an army of its own... Together they traveled and conquered the depths...<br><br><br>And eventually came their offspring, Lesser Lichs, each with its own passion on the afterlife!<br><br><br>You are the youngest son, following your burning desire to be a TOWERMANCER!",
